--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) PREREQUISITES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Python 2.x (> 2.7.3) or 3.x (> 3.3.0)
http://www.python.org/download/

* Python Win32 extensions
http://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32/files/pywin32/Build%20218/
and choose the version corresponding to the previously installed Python version

* PdfCreator (> 1.6.2)
http://fr.pdfforge.org/download

* Microsoft Office (see compatibility matrix)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) INSTALLATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

a) Once all the prerequisites are installed
b) Launch "main.py" located in the 'src/' folder with help of the python 
interpreter
c) That's it! You should be able to see the connections by watching the console
logs

